Package garden_simulator.simulation.plants

Class PlantsPositions

java.lang.Object
garden_simulator.simulation.plants.PlantsPositions
public class PlantsPositions
extends java.lang.Object
Keeps all Plants with their positions. Checks which Plants can reproduce and which should die. Evaluates impacts of Animals and Weather on every plant.
